
list of 'setting' bmessages
each with:
    name = name of the setting (this is more an ID)
        (if the name is 'app_sig' it's a special setting)
    description = desc of the setting (this is more a label)
    type:
        B_STRING_TYPE
            Selector of possible values:
                add a set of "valid_value" keys and a "default" to set the default value
            Free text:
                add 'multi_line' (bool) if multiline
                add 'is_secret' (bool) for password (?)
        B_INT32_TYPE